THS Scholarship Crawfish Boil
May 3 at 6:43 PM ¬∑

We are happy to announce that the fundraiser has been rescheduled for Saturday, May 30th at 4pm. We need the communities help to make the event successful. We will need donations of silent and live auction items and we will need volunteers to help with the event. The ‚ÄúM‚Äù Club is hosting the event and all money raised goes to The Student Foundation Scholarship Fund. With the current circumstances, we are uncertain of the availability of crawfish. The plan is to get them if we can, but food (BBQ for sure) will be provided at the event. As soon as we know the status on crawfish we will update the food plan. Ticket prices remain the same. Our goal is to raise funds for future scholarships, and we appreciate the communities support in helping make it happen. Y‚Äôall get ready to have a great time while supporting Tarkington graduates!! Do not have to be present to be able to help support the fundraiser üôÇ ***please share post so we can reach as many people as possible***

We will need donations of silent and live auction items and we will need volunteers to help with the event. The ‚ÄúM‚Äù Club is hosting the event and all money raised goes to The Student Foundation Scholarship Fund. With the current circumstances, we are uncertain of the availability of crawfish. The plan is to get them if we can, but food (BBQ for sure) will be provided at the event. As soon as we know the status on crawfish we will update the food plan. Ticket prices remain the same. Our goal is to raise funds for future scholarships, and we appreciate the communities support in helping make it happen. Y‚Äôall get ready to have a great time while supporting Tarkington graduates!!
